@startuml l2_activity
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

title **Level 2 — Activity Diagram (Three-Agent Pipeline)**

|Client|
start
:Submit business question;

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager (qwen3:8b)|
:Receive client question;
:Decompose into workstreams\n& sub-questions;
:Create analysis plan (JSON);
note right
  **Tools:** none
  **Cannot:** research, analyze, write report
end note

|#E8F5E9|Market Researcher (qwen3:14b)|
:Receive question + analysis plan;
:Research loop (max 8 rounds):
  search_web() → read_document();
:Synthesize findings into\nstructured Market Analysis JSON;
note right
  **Tools:** search_web(), read_document()
  **Cannot:** do financials, assess risks
end note

|#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant (qwen3:32b)|
:Receive question + plan +\nmarket analysis;
:Synthesize into consulting report\nwith options & tradeoffs;
:Stream report tokens via SSE;
note right
  **Tools:** none (reads context only)
  **Cannot:** search for new info
end note

|#FFFDE7|Evaluator (gemini-2.5-flash)|
:Score report on 6-criterion rubric;
:Produce evaluation scorecard;

|Client|
:Receive report + evaluation scorecard;
stop

@enduml
